<chapter id="faq">
<title>Frequently Asked Questions</title>

<qandaset>

<qandaentry>
<question>
<para>
I'm not sure where to shoot, can I get a hint?
</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para>
No, there is no hint system in &i18n-knavalbattle;.
</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question>
<para>
How can I rotate a ship?
</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para>
Move the ship where you want to place it, then press the &RMB;.
</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question>
<para>
Can I change how the game looks?
</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para>
No, the theme is not changeable.
</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

</qandaset>
